        <mxCell id="q9A1Fd1kpW7AazoVWoaI-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;rotation=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Parametric&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;Normally Distributed&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="262.5" x="663.75" y="4" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="q9A1Fd1kpW7AazoVWoaI-6" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=1;strokeWidth=0.5;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;PARAMETRIC &amp;amp; NON-PARAMETRIC&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Both can be used for disfferent purposes. Parametrics are more suitable for Normal Distributed (check CLT) and checks for means, while Nonparametrics are for Non-n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;ormal Distributed (check CLT) and checks for medians&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;. There are cheat equivalencies between them. So:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;- Normal, tidy and without many outliers: Parametrics&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;- Mesy or with outliers: Non-parametrics&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="106" width="350" x="20" y="700" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xCRE8wccOKQfFn8-C-6z-22" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=none;fillStyle=auto;shadow=0;glass=0;align=left;strokeColor=none;perimeterSpacing=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;REGRESSION&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font&gt;or one-way correlation&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Quantitative Predictor*&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;~&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 76, 153), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Quantitative Outcome*&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;*&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Continuos = Discrete with a big spread-range of data.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;cause-and-effect relationships&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
