        <mxCell id="xCRE8wccOKQfFn8-C-6z-153" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;strokeColor=none;strokeWidth=0.5;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px; line-height: 100%;&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;OUTPUTS&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;p-value&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;(Probability Value):&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The probability that the results happened by random chance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;If&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;p &amp;lt; 0.05&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;: The relationship is statistically significant (we reject the null hypothesis).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;If&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;p &amp;gt; 0.05&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9px; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;: The relationship is likely due to chance (not significant).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(26, 28, 30); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 100%; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;R-squared (R2)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 9px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;A number between 0 and 1 (or 0% to 100%).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 9px; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;It tells you the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 9px; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;percentage of the variance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(26, 28, 30), rgb(212, 214, 216)); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 9px; box-sizing: border-box; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;explained.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
