        <mxCell id="ttZCbK3ra_AwcMFaCHn2-62" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;stat, p_value = stats.t_test_ind (sample1, sample2, &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;alternative&lt;/b&gt;= &#39;greater&#39;&lt;/font&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;H0: sample1 = sample2 |&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: x-small; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;H0: p&amp;gt;0.05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px; line-height: 100%; color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font&gt;H1&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: sample1 != sample2 |&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;H1: p&amp;lt;0.05&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50.3" width="310" x="1340" y="149.7" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ttZCbK3ra_AwcMFaCHn2-80" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ANOVA&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;this test only detects if there is significance, but doesn&#39;t tell exactly in what combinations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;For this, we need to use Post-Hoc tests, bcause they take into account that other tests to combinations are being done, and control the accumulation of risk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="150" x="1250.83" y="261" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ttZCbK3ra_AwcMFaCHn2-83" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1&lt;/b&gt; - Run ANOVA: if p&amp;lt;0.05, continue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2&lt;/b&gt;- Run Tukey&#39;s HSD: check the different p-value of the combinations. If p value &amp;lt; 0.05, the combination is significant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(215, 58, 73); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;from&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; statsmodels.stats.multicomp &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(215, 58, 73); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; pairwise_tukeyhsd&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;tukey &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 92, 197); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; pairwise_tukeyhsd(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 76, 153), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgb(15, 15, 16);&quot;&gt;endog&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgb(0, 92, 197); animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;Outcomes list&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgb(215, 58, 73); animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;groups&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgb(0, 92, 197); animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;Predictors_list&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;, alpha&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 92, 197); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 92, 197); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none !important; transition: none !important;&quot;&gt;0.05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(15, 15, 16); font-family: monospace; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;3&lt;/b&gt; - Look at the means for directions. If Mean sample1&amp;gt; Mean sample2, then sample1 is bigger or outperformed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="174" width="241.66" x="1409.1699999999998" y="215.99999999999997" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ttZCbK3ra_AwcMFaCHn2-84" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;1- Run MANOVA: if Wilks&#39; Lambda p-value&amp;lt; 0.05, continue&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;2 - Split into ANOVA tests:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 76, 153);&quot;&gt;outcomes&lt;/b&gt;= [&amp;lt;list of outcomes&amp;gt;]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;predictors&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;=&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;[&amp;lt;list of predictors&amp;gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 76, 153); font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;outcome&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 76, 153); font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;outcomes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;predictor&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;predictors&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;model = ols (f&#39;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 76, 153), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;outcome&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;} ~&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;{&lt;/font&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;predictor&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(153, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;}&#39;, data=df).fit()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;apply Bonferroni Correction, if the p_value is significant (p &amp;lt; 0.05/quantity of outcomes), &lt;b&gt;proceed to the ANOVA step 2 on the left&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="240" x="1410" y="395.85" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
